    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/d930d7ecfe767d5ef4846e03e1adb05c.poster.avif?t=1761224993\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/d930d7ecfe767d5ef4846e03e1adb05c.webm?t=1761224993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/d930d7ecfe767d5ef4846e03e1adb05c.mp4?t=1761224993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是《荒野守护者崛起》的试玩版，这是一款Roguelite RPG弹幕游戏，在游戏中你将驯服并训练一支多样化的守护灵兽队伍，抵御入侵的怪物大军。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/24c7b821d3937e4cac475ca0974b649a.poster.avif?t=1761224993\" width=600 height=127 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/24c7b821d3937e4cac475ca0974b649a.webm?t=1761224993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在游戏中，你将面对灵感来源于鸟山明和吉姆·亨森世界的手绘奇幻怪物。  <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本次试玩中，你将体验前1到2小时的内容，包括首张地图、10种不同的守护灵兽以及2位可操作角色。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>弹幕天堂</strong> | 在弹幕模式中消灭成千上万的怪物<br></li><li><strong>收集生物</strong> | 发现、驯服并训练魔法生物<br></li><li><strong>构筑队伍</strong> | 使用不同的守护灵兽创建连携效果<br></li><li><strong>Roguelike体验</strong> | 可使用不同的武器和自然守护者进行游戏<br></li><li><strong>进度系统</strong> | 解锁新的守护兽和物品，逐步强化自身<br></li><li><strong>RPG元素</strong> | 探索充满幻想英雄和魔法怪物的多彩世界</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/55d979d053ba91c82d07f584e39cc3b0.poster.avif?t=1761224993\" width=400 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184800/extras/55d979d053ba91c82d07f584e39cc3b0.webm?t=1761224993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >认识开发者</h2>Lioncode Games是由两人组成的独立游戏团队，正通过抢先体验阶段制作《荒野守护者崛起》，以便通过社区反馈拓展游戏内容。",
